OL,7,FMany pharmacists in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fare having to dip into their own
OL,9,Fsavings and pensions to ensure the
OL,10,Fsupply of medicines.
OL,12,FCommunity Pharmacy Northern Ireland is
OL,13,Fwarning that medicine supply could be
OL,14,Fat risk if urgent funding isn't put in
OL,15,Fplace by the Department of Health.
OL,17,FThe Department funds community
OL,18,Fpharmacies across the country but many
OL,19,Freport that their costs aren't being
OL,20,Fcovered.
