OL,7,FOwner of Dundela Pharmacy on the
OL,8,FBelmont Road in east Belfast, David
OL,9,FMcCrea, told UTV in his 30 years of
OL,10,Frunning the business, the last year
OL,11,Fhas been the worst.
OL,13,F"We have to buy in the drugs, that's a
OL,14,Fcost to us and when we dispense them
OL,15,Fthe Department reimburse us but the
OL,16,Fprice that they're paying us doesn't
OL,17,Fcover the cost of the drugs in a lot
OL,18,Fof cases.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/9
