OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"It's not sustainable and that is why
OL,8,Fwe've reached this crisis point. There
OL,9,Fare pharmacists who are struggling to
OL,10,Fpay their wholesale bills and they're
OL,11,Fhaving to put in their own money to
OL,12,Fcover their costs to pay their bills
OL,13,Fand pay their staff.
OL,15,F"The bottom line is if we can't pay
OL,16,Four wholesalers, the supply of
OL,17,Fmedicines will stop."
