OL,7,FRepresentatives from Community
OL,8,FPharmacy NI brought their concerns
OL,9,Fbefore Stormont's Health Committee on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,FChief Executive of CPNI, Gerard
OL,13,FGreene, told the committee: "The risks
OL,14,Fare such that the ability of community
OL,15,Fpharmacies to maintain its very basic
OL,16,Ffunction of the supply of medicines to
OL,17,Fthe public can no longer be assumed.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/9
