OL,7,F"Without further intervention, which
OL,8,Fis what we are seeking your support
OL,9,Fin, the community pharmacy funding
OL,10,Fdeficit will widen further."
OL,12,FIn a statement, the Department of
OL,13,FHealth said it "recognises the
OL,14,Ffundamental role that Community
OL,15,FPharmacies have been carrying out".
