OL,7,FIt added: "The Department remains
OL,8,Fcommitted to working with CPNI on
OL,9,Fcommissioning arrangements within the
OL,10,Fexisting Ministerial mandate and
OL,11,Ffinancial envelope. However, it is
OL,12,Fimportant to emphasise that the
OL,13,FDepartment is facing a significant
OL,14,Ffunding gap to maintain existing
OL,15,Fservices, with the HSC continuing to
OL,16,Fface an extremely unpredictable and
OL,17,Fvolatile position.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/9
