OL,7,F"Despite these challenges, the
OL,8,FDepartment has provided additional in
OL,9,Fyear investment to support community
OL,10,Fpharmacy worth #14.9m, including a
OL,11,Fsuspension of discount clawback in
OL,12,FNovember 2023 worth #4.8m, plus
OL,13,Finvestment in February 2024 of #6.1m
OL,14,Frelating to inflationary pressures and
OL,15,F#4m associated with service pressures
OL,16,Frelated to medicines adherence
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/9
