OL,7,F"The Department has also provided CPNI
OL,8,Fwith a commitment to undertake a
OL,9,Freview of financial framework for
OL,10,Fcommunity pharmacy services,
OL,11,Fconsidering the position elsewhere in
OL,12,Fthe UK and affordability within the NI
OL,13,Fcontext.
OL,15,F"The Department remains keen to
OL,16,Fcontinue to have a collaborative
OL,17,Frelationship with CPNI, based on
OL,18,Frealistic expectations around what we
OL,19,Fcan commission and fund, and to do
OL,20,Fthis through open and honest dialogue,
OL,21,Fas we have done to date."
